      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. This is the perfect find for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great pulling into the driveway. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
